Exercise 4.12: The popular web comic xkcd has a JSON interface. 
For example, a request to https://xkcd.com/571/info.0.json produces a detailed
description of comic 571, one of many favorites. Download each URL (once!) and 
build an offline index. Write a tool xkcd that, using this index, prints the URL
and transcript of each comic that matches a search term provided on the command line.

Exercise 4.13: The JSON-based web service of the Open Movie Database lets you 
search https://omdbapi.com/ for a movie by name and dow nlo ad its poster image . Write a tool
poster that down loads the poster image for the movie named on the command line.